@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <div id="policy-container"class=" card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p class="text-muted">Last Updated: <strong>2025-02-18</strong></p>

            <h2 class="mt-4">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to <strong>The Guitarist’s Toolkit</strong>. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when using our website and services.</p>

            <h2 class="mt-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you register, we collect your name, email address, and username.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Authentication Data:</strong> Your password is securely hashed and stored.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about your practice sessions, setlists, and interactions with the application.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Cookies & Session Data:</strong> We use cookies and sessions to enhance user experience and maintain authentication.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="mt-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item">Manage user authentication and accounts.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Track practice sessions and manage setlists.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Improve application functionality and user experience.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Secure your data and prevent unauthorized access.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="mt-4">4. Data Protection & Security</h2>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item">Passwords are stored using <strong>secure hashing techniques (BCrypt)</strong>.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">User sessions are managed securely via <strong>cookies</strong> with appropriate expiration settings.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">We <strong>do not</strong> share, sell, or trade your data with third parties.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="mt-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                <li class="list-group-item">Request access to your data.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Update or delete your profile.</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">Opt-out of non-essential data collection.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="mt-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated through the application.</p>

            <h2 class="mt-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>For any questions regarding this policy, please contact us at <a href="https://github.com/logan-tolbert">GitHub</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
